South Florida Compendium (Working Title)

The SoFLo Compendium uses glitch photogrammetry to catalog various objects of power, auratic spaces, and angelic entities throughout Miami and Broward County.

Works are a collaboration with the artist's 15-year-old brother Joshua, who created many of the 3D scans.
